{"tid":200804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓外務省副相：美若想戰必定奉陪","createTime":"2017-04-14T09:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T15:13:26.000Z","uid":28366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8e29a122dc07d63e89e330f8047bd70141bf12","tid":200804,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20170414/25610252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20170414%2F25610252.jpg&h=9c471781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美國派遣原本靠港新加坡的美國海軍「卡爾文森號」航空母艦打擊群駛向朝鮮半島近海，以加強對北韓施壓。（<a href=\"http://圖取自卡爾文森號臉書facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AA%E5%8D%A1%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E6%A3%AE%E8%99%9F%E8%87%89%E6%9B%B8facebook.com&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=dd69807b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自卡爾文森號臉書facebook.com</a>）</span><br />\n<br />\n（中央社平壤14日綜合外電報導）北韓外務省副相（相當於外交次長）韓成烈今天放話，指川普領導的美國變得更惡毒與好鬥。他聲稱將在「有必要的時間和地點」第6度核試，並揚言若美國選擇開戰，北韓一定奉陪。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，韓成烈（Han Song Ryol）今天批評美國總統川普製造朝鮮半島緊張的「惡性循環」，並指川普的「挑釁」推文才「製造麻煩」。<br />\n<br />\n韓成烈指美國在川普領導下，比以前歐巴馬當總統時「更加惡毒與好鬥」。他說：「現在我們比較（美國）前政府與川普對朝鮮民主主義人民共和國（DPRK，北韓正式國名）的政策，我們的結論是美國變得更惡毒也更好鬥。不管美國政治人物說什麼，只要是意在推翻DPRK的體制與政府，我們都斷然拒絕。」<br />\n<br />\n韓成烈今天在平壤接受美聯社獨家專訪時，就美國對北韓的軍事挑釁提出警告，稱「如果他們選擇開戰，我們一定奉陪」。<br />\n<br />\n韓成烈受訪時說：「如果美國進行魯莽的軍事演習，我們就會以DPRK先發制人的打擊加以對抗。我們已有威力十足的核嚇阻。面對美國先發制人攻擊，我們當然不會只將雙臂交叉。」<br />\n<br />\n40分鐘的專訪裡，韓成烈透過北韓外交部提供的傳譯，平靜、文雅但堅定地傳達訊息。<br />\n<br />\n美國派航空母艦到朝鮮半島外海海域，並與南韓進行史上最大規模的聯合軍演，加深緊張態勢。平壤最近才試射1枚彈道飛彈，部分專家指北韓事實上隨時可能再展開另一次核試。<br />\n<br />\n談及將是北韓第6次核試的時候，韓成烈說：「這由我們總部來決定，在總部認為有必要的時間和地點，就會進行。」（譯者：中央社陳亦偉）1060414<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201704140229-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201704140229-1.aspx&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9323c2de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201704140229-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c9300333662d461015d47caf18262b91eb25fe53","tid":200804,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5573d1cd7341940bb4e676c44962ef5eb64361","tid":200804,"uid":35236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"仲咁口硬,掃定午餐肉同花生先"},{"pid":"5c6fb243fe13adc324b7e21c7fd9ce7d7009d0d0","tid":200804,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"你唔好一味得個up，做啦仆街"},{"pid":"ad95d6d40020be76b232858b1f12be1d9272c9a4","tid":200804,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"今次一定打硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd24f24f9fa338b628b2684d4c698310073b1fc","tid":200804,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"你打還打咪撚用核武 搞撚到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6abe4e4de44123f44b696ff52233356ff4007c","tid":200804,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d236c141b12a51e9358a1f944ba4e9c8ddcbbd57","tid":200804,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19f558d705983bda95233b020bba45a0b1a64dc","tid":200804,"uid":9